    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The perfect hand of Nostalpix（像素王牌）是一个1989年经典电子卡牌游戏的重制版。收集，升级并进化卡牌，构筑你的完美卡组，运用经典招式亦或是崭新机制来击败你的敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345540/extras/c446cb402ad6224e0c9217b132d5eb90.gif?t=1769005373\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345540/extras/c446cb402ad6224e0c9217b132d5eb90.poster.avif?t=1769005373\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主宰你的对局</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握游戏机制和战术，用多种能力和诡计困住你的对手：怪兽，宝珠，符文...现在你知道谁是老大了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与CARD NOVA HYPER 共享同一宇宙观</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戏剧性到<strong>爆衣</strong> 的卡牌游戏，现在就加入愿望单并加入众筹吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构筑你的卡组</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合各种卡牌打造您的最强卡组!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选取怪兽时，请留意配以合适的符文。再结合你的战术选择最强力的宝珠，你将所向披靡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定制你的卡牌</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好好考虑如何升级，进化或觉醒卡牌！用多种多样的符文来定制它们的效果，寻找最好、最贴合你的玩法的导向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切都是为了追寻“最完美的像素王牌”。</p>",
